    public class AlbumPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener
    Album display screen, shows all photos in album and allows album level operations like recaptioning photos, moving photos between albums, and deleting photos from album

    Ananth Rao, Allon Fineziber
